  "comment": "$$tg\\alpha=\\frac{\\sin\\alpha}{\\cos\\alpha}$$\nНайдем синус угла:\n$$1=\\cos^2\\alpha+\\sin^2\\alpha\\\\ sin^2\\alpha=1-\\frac{25\\cdot 26}{26^2}=1-\\frac{25}{26}=\\frac{1}{26}\\\\ \\sin\\alpha=\\pm\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{26}}$$\nТак как \\(\\alpha \\in (0; \\frac{\\pi}{2})\\) \\(\\sin\\alpha=\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{26}}\\)\n$$tg\\alpha=\\frac{26\\cdot 1}{5\\sqrt{26}\\cdot\\sqrt{26}}=\\frac{1}{5}=0,2$$\nОтвет: 0,2",
